# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TRELLIS.2 demo artifacts
# Keep ONLY what's needed to view demo.html:
#   - demo.html / setup.md / run_doubao_rgba.py
#   - doubao_rgba.png (background-removed input)
#   - doubao_v2.glb   (final 3D asset, referenced by demo.html)
# Everything else under repo root is treated as reproducible / scratch.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# 3D / media outputs at repo root — ignore by default ...
/*.glb
/*.mp4
/*.3mf
/*.obj
/*.ply
/*.stl
/*.fbx
/*.usdz

# ... but explicitly KEEP the deliverables shown by demo.html
!/doubao_v2.glb
!/doubao_rgba.png

# Throwaway scripts at repo root (only keep run_doubao_rgba.py, the canonical entry)
/run_doubao.py
/glb_to_bambu_3mf.py
/tmp_*.py
/scratch_*.py
/*.log

# Logs / tunnels / local server state
/tmp/
*.pid
nohup.out

